									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">This article is about war in general; for other uses of the term, see <a href="/wiki/War_(disambiguation)" title="War (disambiguation)">war (disambiguation)</a> and <a href="/wiki/The_War" title="The War">The War</a>.</div>
<div class="dablink">"Warring" redirects here. For the American boxer, see <a href="/wiki/James_Warring" title="James Warring">James Warring</a>.</div>
