<li><a href="/wiki/Biological_warfare" title="Biological warfare">Biological warfare</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Mine_warfare" title="Mine warfare">Mine warfare</a> a type of static terrain denial warfare</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Air_warfare" title="Air warfare" class="mw-redirect">Air warfare</a> that includes Airborne warfare and Airmobile warfare</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Sub-aquatic_warfare" title="Sub-aquatic warfare" class="mw-redirect">Sub-aquatic warfare</a></li>
