<li><a href="/wiki/Cyber_warfare" title="Cyber warfare" class="mw-redirect">Cyber warfare</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Directed-energy_warfare" title="Directed-energy warfare">Directed-energy warfare</a></li>
