<li>30,000,000–60,000,000 - <a href="/wiki/Mongol_Empire" title="Mongol Empire">Mongol Conquests</a> (13th century) (see <a href="/wiki/Mongol_invasions" title="Mongol invasions" class="mw-redirect">Mongol invasions</a> and <a href="/wiki/Tatar_invasions" title="Tatar invasions">Tatar invasions</a>)<sup id="cite_ref-52" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-52" title=""><span>[</span>53<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-53" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-53" title=""><span>[</span>54<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-54" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-54" title=""><span>[</span>55<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-55" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-55" title=""><span>[</span>56<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
<li>25,000,000 - <a href="/wiki/Manchu" title="Manchu">Manchu</a> conquest of <a href="/wiki/Ming_China" title="Ming China" class="mw-redirect">Ming China</a> (1616–1662)<sup id="cite_ref-56" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-56" title=""><span>[</span>57<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
