<li>5,000,000–9,000,000 - <a href="/wiki/Russian_Civil_War" title="Russian Civil War">Russian Civil War and Foreign Intervention</a> (1917–1921)<sup id="cite_ref-62" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-62" title=""><span>[</span>63<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
