<li>217,000 - 1,124,303 - <a href="/wiki/War_on_Terror" title="War on Terror" class="mw-redirect">War on Terror</a> (9/11/2001-Present)<sup class="noprint Template-Fact"><span title="This claim needs references to reliable sources&#160;since February 2009" style="white-space: nowrap;">[<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed" title="Wikipedia:Citation needed">citation needed</a></i>]</span></sup></li>
<li>200,000 - 1,000,000<sup id="cite_ref-82" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-82" title=""><span>[</span>83<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-83" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-83" title=""><span>[</span>84<span>]</span></a></sup> - <a href="/wiki/Albigensian_Crusade" title="Albigensian Crusade">Albigensian Crusade</a> (1208-1259)</li>
